-  `/Users/guest1/Documents/SAVI-iOS/Docs/Design/FolderPolishArchive/2026-05-02-before-folder-palette-image-background/`
-- Softened the light-mode folder palette through the shared
-  `SaviFolderVisualStyle` path so Home folder tiles, All Folders grid tiles, and
-  folder list rows keep their playful color identity while blending more calmly
-  with the compact editorial Home screen.
