-  opacity so icons remain useful without competing as hard with folder names.
-- Added a persisted `uses_image_background` folder setting and editor toggle so
-  a chosen/searched folder image can become the whole folder card background,
-  with SAVI applying a readability overlay and falling back to the color card if
-  no image exists.
